added.description: Mifune calls for the formation of the Allied Shinobi Forces to counter the Akatsuki and proposes the Hokage to lead them.
added.title: A Painful Decision

added.description: Naruto learns from Sai that Sakura intends to kill Sasuke. The Sand arrive to brief the Leaf Ninja about what happened at the Five Kage Summit.
added.title: As One's Friend

added.description: Pirates living on an island resembling a battleship open fire on Naruto's ship. Using Yamato's Wood Style Jutsu, Naruto and the others escape into an undersea cave.
added.title: Battleship Island

added.description: Danzo believes he's won the battle against Sasuke. Little does he realize, Sasuke placed him under genjutsu before they last exchanged blows.
added.title: Danzo Shimura

added.description: Kakashi decides to go after Sakura to stop her, while Yamato and Naruto are ordered to return to the Leaf Village.
added.title: Danzo's Right Arm

added.description: By resurrecting the monster Ten Tails and becoming its Jinchuriki Host, Madara plots to bring the entire world under his Genjutsu control.
added.title: Declaration of War

added.description: Naruto and the other crew members find their ship infested with poisonous mushrooms. To make matters worse, the mushrooms have destroyed all of their food and supplies, making their voyage into one of survival.

input: Eat or Die! Mushrooms from Hell

added.title: Eat or Die! Mushrooms from Hell

added.description: Naruto, Yamato, and Kakashi follow Team Samui in the hopes of meeting the Raikage and asking him to spare Sasuke's life.
added.title: Enter the Five Kage!

added.description: Guy recalls the celebration after Lee learned the Hidden Lotus technique.
added.title: Fight! Rock Lee!

added.description: Having become a high-level shinobi, Naruto is now able to understand Sasuke's heart, and he tells Sasuke to direct all of his hatred towards him.
added.title: High-Level Shinobi

added.description: Bee believes Samehada has taken a liking to him but is unaware that this is all just part of the Akatsuki's plan.
added.title: Infiltrator

added.description: Naruto gathers his friends and tells them that he will defeat Sasuke alone. Meanwhile, the Elders of the Leaf officially nominate Kakashi to become the next Hokage.
added.title: Kakashi Hatake, the Hokage

added.description: Realizing what it means to gain something precious and then lose it, Naruto sneaks out of the inn to follow Sakura and Kakashi to find Sasuke.
added.title: Lost Bonds

added.description: The Five Kage assemble in the Land of Iron to hold the Five Kage Summit Conference.
added.title: Naruto's Plea

added.description: Having blocked the combined attacks of Gaara, Temari, Kankuro, and Darui with his Susano'o, Sasuke goes after Danzo.
added.title: Power of the Five Kage

added.description: In Mount Myoboku, Gerotora, Fukasaku, and the Great Lord Elder are debating whether to give Naruto the key to the Tetragram Seal left behind by Jiraiya, an act that could unleash the Nine Tails.

input: Prophecy of the Great Lord Elder

added.title: Prophecy of the Great Lord Elder

added.description: Madara makes a sudden appearance before Naruto and reveals the truth behind Itachi's actions.
added.title: Racing Lightning

added.description: Naruto's Shadow Clones turn against him after feeling mistreated and overworked. Unable to undo his jutsu, Naruto is taken captive.
added.title: Revenge of the Shadow Clones

added.description: Sakura arrives in the Land of Iron to speak with Naruto, but her confession surprises him. Elsewhere, Kisame appears before Killer Bee.
added.title: Sakura's Feelings

added.description: As Sakura heads toward Sasuke, she begins to recollect fond memories of Team 7.
added.title: Sakura's Resolve

added.description: In the Land of Iron, Sasuke and the Raikage fight a battle to the death when Gaara, the Kazekage, intervenes.
added.title: Sasuke's Ninja Way

added.description: At Mount Myoboku, Naruto prepares to store Gerotora within himself, but hesitates as it also holds the potential risk of unleashing the Nine Tails.
added.title: Storage

added.description: Sakura tells Sasuke that she wants to desert the village and join him. A skeptical Sasuke tells Sakura he will believe her if she can finish off Karin.
added.title: The Burden

added.description: As he prepares for the coming war, Shikamaru begins to feel the pressure of having to shoulder the lives of his friends.
added.title: The Closed Route

added.description: Naruto's ship is stranded at sea, when another ship suddenly appears. Believing it to be a ghost ship, Naruto panics until he finds Hishaku, a sailor, on board.
added.title: The Cursed Ghost Ship

added.description: Karui and Omoi of the Hidden Cloud press Naruto to give up information regarding Sasuke. Naruto realizes their motives, but decides he cannot sell out his friend.

input: The Eve of the Five Kage Summit
Eve of the Five Kage Summit

added.title: The Eve of the Five Kage Summit

added.description: The formation of the Allied Shinobi Forces is ratified by the Feudal Lords of the Five Great Nations. Each Kage returns to their village to prepare for the coming war.
added.title: The Five Great Nations Mobilize

added.description: The Five Kage assemble in the Hidden Cloud Village to discuss where to hide the remaining two Jinchuriki.
added.title: The Five Kage's Decision

added.description: Danzo's uncanny jutsu prevents Sasuke from landing a clean hit on his enemy. As Karin attempts to analyze Danzo's jutsu, Madara recognizes it as Izanagi, the Uchiha's Forbidden Visual Jutsu.
added.title: The Forbidden Visual Jutsu

added.description: Naruto, Yamato, and Aoba arrive on an island where they spot a young woman. While trying to gather information, Aoba learns of a horrible secret hidden on the island.
added.title: The Forgotten Island

added.description: During their voyage, Naruto, Yamato, Gai, and Aoba stop at an island to recover from severe seasickness. There, they unexpectedly meet up with Sakura, Ino, and Choji.
added.title: The Ninja of Benisu

added.description: The news of Danzo becoming Hokage and issuing orders to dispose of Sasuke reaches Naruto and Sakura. The two decide to confront Danzo, only to be halted by Kakashi.
added.title: The Sixth Hokage Danzo

added.description: Killer Bee engages in a deadly battle against Kisame, who has come to capture the Eight-Tails.

Beast vs. The Tailless Tailed Beast

input: The Young Man and the Sea
